Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, somewhere along the way, \Nit's gotten all spring-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this weird feeling like \Nthe season suddenly changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't help but sense \Nthe will of some being,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,similar to the invisible hand of God...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to \Nlife here at the estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tiger shouldn't suddenly start \Ntalking, right from the intro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll confuse the non-productive \Nmembers of society
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who just started watching the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about them. Think about the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you got a problem with me talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Class 2 real estate broker \Nand a licensed boiler engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real estate broker?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't tell the Miss and \Nthe others than I can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, in terms of a Pokémon analogy, \Nwhich celebrated its 10th anniversary,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm technically the Pikachu of this show,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's about the image. \NThe image is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting like you're a respectable mascot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a lame PR character!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you think you can boost \Nthe economy by tens of billions of yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! Wh-Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I a lame PR character?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but a certain \Npopular weekly boys' manga magazine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had me ranked 12th in popularity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even at the autograph session in Nagoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The last character to be requested \Non an art board was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's going \Nout somewhere for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me. I'll return without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, I do not really want to go, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:27.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where could the Miss be headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:31.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a fateful parting for Hayate and Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:38.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:42.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:44.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:46.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:50.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:54.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, you damn butler-in-debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:07.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:07.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:14.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:14.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:22.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:22.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:26.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:26.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:35.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:35.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:45.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:45.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:51.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:51.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:03.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:03.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:10.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:10.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:17.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:17.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My First Errand\N~This Is Snake. No Response.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, it seems the Miss has \Nleft on a rare outing somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Somewhere?" She went to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's obviously a school-age child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, but ever since \NI came to this estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally thought she was receiving \Na special education from tutors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she is... How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a touch of you-know-what...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acute societal withdrawal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's mid-April already, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the school sent a notice, saying \Nshe should attend once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Incidentally, which \Nschool does she attend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's technically a student \Nat Hakuou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou is where all the rich kids go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a super famous school \Nthat covers grades 1-12!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing she is, is smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi's lunch. She forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is part of my duties as a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in modern day Tokyo here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:47.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place just might be \Nbigger than Suginami Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding the Miss in there \Nis going to be difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to work hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a Hakuou student, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?! Identify yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you a teacher here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm Miss Nagi Sanzenin's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that you're Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may have no chest, but \Nshe's still a girl! A {\i1}girl{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are limits to lies and \Ncredit cards, you know! Limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that is not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Miss's butler, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible cosmos...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What butler has such a look \Nof poverty about him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there may be some out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never seen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make a point of only believing \Nwhat I've seen myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it?! I mean, do you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a duty to protect this school \Nfrom suspicious individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because I can't afford to \Nhave my salary docked any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're a suspicious individual! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have an important duty to \Ndeliver this lunch to the Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's a clash of duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me at least get your name first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not introducing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because it's personal information!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping your personal information safe \Nis common sense in this modern age!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it, Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle has already begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I don't really understand, \Nbut that was cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just looks like Katsy's \Nin fine form again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that hapless looking kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give it up, Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not capable of getting past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The background has turned into \Nanother dimension for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could this be the legendary Drunken Fist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I don't think that's quite it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I need to get past this person \Nat all costs and get into the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Into the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Into the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What do you know? I've \Nalready gotten past you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd switched places before I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! That didn't count! It didn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no idiot would actually wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when told to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends of all ages watching this anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Miki Hanabishi, a \Nstudent of this Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Izumi Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Haruo Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm Risa Asakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show up out of the blue
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and start promoting yourself to \Npeople outside the picture tube!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your classes anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Picture tube"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon, but surely this disturbance \Nis more important than any classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Picture tube"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What is this? The Showa era?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want our help, Katsy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. I picked up this habit from \Nwhen debt collectors were after me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ran away without thinking, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:26.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandarin Oranges
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not actually a suspicious \Nindividual in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I should act boldly and \Nfearlessly. Boldy and fearlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am now a butler \Nof the Sanzenin family!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That clock tower sure is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've come all this way, I'd \Nlove to climb to the top just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only members of the student council
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are allowed at the top of the clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you? Where in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what a Sanzenin family butler \Nis doing in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing \Nin a place like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Sanzenin family butler for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting no time getting \Nto the crux of the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, climbing trees is all \Nthe rage at Hakuou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this look like I'm having fun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! You don't need to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... you know, one of {\i1}those{\i0} situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trees aren't as slippery as you might think
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and with the branches, they're \Npretty easy to climb,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when you're only looking up you \Nneglect to look down, if you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, the cat has a \Ngreat time getting up the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but finds itself unable to get \Ndown... Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put it so simply! It \Nmakes it sound like I'm a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, they say fools and smoke \Nlike to get up to high places,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not a fool, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one said you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Sanzenin family butler, \Nyou have decent reflexes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:04.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, why does she know \Nthat I'm the new Sanzenin butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a little favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ca...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't catch me properly. \NThat was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think it's dangerous, please \Ndon't jump in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to yell at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really scared and I wanted \Nto get down as quick as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of heights...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's unseemly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a girl! In a skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wearing bike shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl should behave more modestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with this naïve attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Sanzenin family butlers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have the emotional sophistication \Nof a grade schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're mocking me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you didn't have to jump so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've come to your \Nrescue if you'd just asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so I just have to \Nask to get rescued, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't like high places, \Nwhat were you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Well, I didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that little one had fallen \Nfrom his nest and he was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this day and age,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you climbed a tree you couldn't get \Ndown from for a reason like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Making fun of me again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just thinking you're a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me for all the rude things I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, that chick can rest easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you stupid thing! \NWhat's up with that crow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! You might hit the chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so beautiful parental \Nlove will save the chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They're going to abandon him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mother and father abandoning \Ntheir own child...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's never okay to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Crow, would you please leave it at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll have to hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you told me not to throw \Nit, but you did it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have good control, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... What's that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like I have no control!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get so hungry \Nwhen you're in your youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What might this pretty girl's name be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leaving the mystery and suspicions for later,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to be continued in the second half!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dried seaweed.\N({\u1}Nori{\u0})
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lymph.\N({\u1}Ri{\u0}n{\u1}pa{\u0})
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hayate is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he should be over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you not seen him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this school is as \Nvast as Vana'diel, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Hayate lovingly made \Na packed lunch for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Not to worry, I will \Nbe sure to accept Hayate's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... "lovingly"? I'm the one who made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where could Hayate be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what could he be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so your name is Miss Hinagiku Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as part of my thanks, want \Nme to take you to the top of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I thought only members of \Nthe student council can go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the president \Nof the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! What idiot decided to put the \Nstudent council office way up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss Katsura, you don't \Nlike high places, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm satisfied with just \Ngetting to see it up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you wanted to go up \Nthere at least once, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find even greater \Nsatisfaction if you go up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't let this chance slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my thanks to you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki, if you don't try to get \Nwhat you want once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll miss your chance at happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, it's so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting the student council \Noffice so high up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like she might be \Na bit like Miss Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the student council president,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's not like this is \Nmy first time up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy shouldn't give such \Na noncommittal answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that... really a suspicious individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that he's a \Nreal Sanzenin family butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So high and mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would a lame bachelor teacher who \Nbuilds Gundam models at school know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! The head spike went somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter anymore if he's \Nreally a suspicious individual or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The illustrious Hakuou Academy allowed \Nsomeone to break in! That's a fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If we don't defeat him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Took the words right out of my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}people's confidence in the \NAcademy's security will plummet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let your guard down around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's supposed to be a teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It'd be terrible if that happened! \NIt would, wouldn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mainly, terrible for my salary, \Nsince I allowed the intruder in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace. Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Miss Segawa, you \Ntake the school building!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hanabishi, the area around the gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Miss Asakaze... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, go search wherever you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And take Yasu with you or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasu... Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:16:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start by searching for the \Nsuspicious individual from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This view is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it? Wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The view from the clock \Ntower is truly magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sheer beauty of it almost makes \Nyou forget to blink, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see it from so far inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I'm viewing it \Nthrough my mind's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really have a great \Nview of the school from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? The reason the student \Ncouncil office is here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is so that we can have a \Ngood view of the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen the view \Nfrom here, Miss Katsura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I listen to my heart, \Nrather than pay heed to my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School seems so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? But class seems to \Nbe in session right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Katsura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, honestly! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no helping it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:17:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Classes started while I was helping Browny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Browny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chick we saved earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a brown sparrow, so he's "Browny".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, talk about simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! It's important to \Nhave easy names in anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I should go deliver \Nthe Miss's lunch soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know where the cafeteria is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, I got to \Nsee an unforgettable view.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You talk as if you'll \Nnever be coming here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's unlikely that I'll ever have \Nanother opportunity, Miss Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Hinagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another Katsura, \Nwho stands out a lot here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so everyone calls me by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So call me Hinagiku. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious individual sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sis"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Sis Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn suspicious individual, \Nmeet your hundred-year doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that it's actually \Nbeen a hundred years...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, yes, I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm going to destroy you immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! He's not a suspicious individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! That doesn't matter anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already explained that earlier \Nto everyone watching this anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil, therefore kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:27.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:28.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to meet your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:35.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CLANG
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Another one of \Nyour nonsensical antics?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've improved your skill, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that won't be enough to stop \Nyour sis's passion and young energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stop pay cuts, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never lost to you in a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I've lost to you in is age,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which you've accumulated \Nwith nothing to show for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be my little sister, but I'm \Nnot forgiving you for that, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When are you paying back the 20,000 \Nyen I loaned you last month?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wha?! Th-That's a cheap shot! \NTaking Yukichi hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I never did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I need to get going soon to \Ndeliver this lunch to the Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yukichi's to be respected, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}His "Encouragement of Learning" \Nsold 3.4 million copies, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, want me to give this back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can you come get it when \Nyou're afraid of heights?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, turn over that suspicious \Nindividual right this minute
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and forget about the 20,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me for a fool, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the student council president \Nof Hakuou Academy, Hinagiku Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treating a guest like a \Nsuspicious individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will absolutely not permit such behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my little sister for you. Then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! It's dangerous \Nto stand there like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanzenin family butlers really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you finally believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing. You were a great help \Nclearing up the misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I need to go deliver \Nthe Miss's lunch soon, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I threw it earlier without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:51.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do? I'm going to be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll make sure \Nto apologize to Nagi, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, maybe I'll apologize, too! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi! Um, there are a lot \Nof reasons for this and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Katsura probably stole the lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when she got up on the railing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a strong gust that \Nalmost caused her to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is when Hayate saved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the lunch paid the price for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What prodigious deductive powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the result is... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you for coming all \Nthis way for me, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I have grown hungry, \Nso this is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going home, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to attend your \Nafternoon classes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver another one straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I won't be able to play hooky...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in tears just a moment ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is part of my job as a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:03.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have the Miss study properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Ayasaki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His infiltration of Hakuou \NAcademy has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, he will fight the comedy boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious individual boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're searching so hard for him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard's quick on his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, and that's how we've gotten \Nto play hooky with impunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We truly owe it all to the \Nsuspicious individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:27.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:27.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:32.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:32.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:38.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:38.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:41.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:41.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:47.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:47.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:53.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:53.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:59.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:59.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:03.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:03.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:09.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:09.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:14.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:14.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:19.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:19.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:30.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:30.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:35.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:35.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:40.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:40.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:44.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:44.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:55.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:55.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:00.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure have great weather again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:19.30,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:01.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering how warm it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe it'll be midsummer by \Nthe time Golden Week is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.19,0:24:05.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:07.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,'Course not, ya fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.85,0:24:09.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya sure have found a fine entertainer, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:11.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a butler, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:13.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:16.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thoughtless Jokes and \NKindness Bring Misfortune."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.18,0:24:20.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend told me that I mustn't carry \Non conversations with strangers,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thoughtless Jokes and \NKindness Bring Misfortune
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.01,0:24:23.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.85,0:24:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
